01:10:57,119 --> 01:11:00,782  X1:341 X2:647 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">You'll be okay.</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">It's just to make you sleep.</font>

732
01:11:00,856 --> 01:11:02,721  X1:281 X2:647 Y1:315 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Target down.</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">Target secure.</font>

733
01:11:02,791 --> 01:11:05,624  X1:071 X2:317 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">I'm going to take you</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">someplace safe.</font>

734
01:11:05,694 --> 01:11:08,925  X1:280 X2:438 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Okay? Bruce?</font>

735
01:11:08,998 --> 01:11:11,432  X1:321 X2:400 Y1:412 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">Bruce?</font>

736
01:11:11,500 --> 01:11:13,491  X1:310 X2:394 Y1:412 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>Bruce?</i></font>

737
01:12:23,339 --> 01:12:25,967  X1:071 X2:367 Y1:411 Y2:439
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>[Man Shouts, Indistinct]</i></font>

738
01:13:47,356 --> 01:13:49,620  X1:455 X2:646 Y1:379 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Man Shouting]</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">Clear!</font>

739
01:13:59,435 --> 01:14:02,165  X1:070 X2:647 Y1:315 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Attention on deck.</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">Carry on.</font>

740
01:14:10,145 --> 01:14:13,046  X1:071 X2:370 Y1:347 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>[Betty]</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>We're buried out here</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>in the middle of nowhere.</i></font>

741
01:14:13,115 --> 01:14:15,515  X1:071 X2:374 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>How long are you</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>gonna keep him sedated?</i></font>

742
01:14:15,584 --> 01:14:17,848  X1:228 X2:490 Y1:379 Y2:438
<font color="#fdfdfd">For the rest of his</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">natural life, if I have to.</font>

743
01:14:17,920 --> 01:14:20,821  X1:070 X2:647 Y1:347 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">You said I could trust you.</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">I'm your father.</font>

744
01:14:20,889 --> 01:14:25,155  X1:309 X2:647 Y1:347 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">You can trust me to do</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">what I think is right,</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">not what you think you want.</font>

745
01:14:25,227 --> 01:14:29,254  X1:202 X2:516 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">- He is a human being.</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">- He is also something else.</font>

746
01:14:29,331 --> 01:14:32,892  X1:161 X2:556 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Suppose he gets out,</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">has one of his little mood swings...</font>

747
01:14:32,968 --> 01:14:34,367  X1:072 X2:299 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">in a populated area.</font>

748
01:14:34,403 --> 01:14:39,033  X1:151 X2:566 Y1:347 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Yes, I'm aware of</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">the potential danger.</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">I'm also aware that he saved my life.</font>

749
01:14:39,107 --> 01:14:42,042  X1:070 X2:308 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Yeah, from a mutant</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">French poodle.</font>

750
01:14:42,110 --> 01:14:44,408  X1:072 X2:400 Y1:411 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">I'm indebted to him for that.</font>

751
01:14:44,480 --> 01:14:48,007  X1:326 X2:647 Y1:347 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">He also put</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">three men in a hospital,</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">and Talbot's barely walking!</font>

752
01:14:48,083 --> 01:14:52,349  X1:184 X2:535 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">- What do you want me to do?</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">- I want you to help him!</font>

753
01:14:52,421 --> 01:14:56,255  X1:136 X2:581 Y1:379 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">- Why is he such a threat to you?</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">- Because I know what he comes from.</font>

754
01:14:56,325 --> 01:15:00,557  X1:204 X2:513 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">He is his father's son,</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">every last molecule of him.</font>

755
01:15:00,629 --> 01:15:03,120  X1:072 X2:360 Y1:379 Y2:439
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>He says he doesn't know</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>his father,</i></font>

756
01:15:03,198 --> 01:15:08,602  X1:149 X2:550 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>but he's workin'in the same</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>exact goddamn field his father did.</i></font>

757
01:15:08,670 --> 01:15:13,004  X1:164 X2:555 Y1:379 Y2:438
<font color="#fdfdfd">So either he's lyin'...</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">or it's somethin' worse, and he's...</font>

758
01:15:13,075 --> 01:15:15,100  X1:315 X2:392 Y1:411 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>What?</i></font>

759
01:15:15,177 --> 01:15:18,977  X1:219 X2:500 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Predestined to follow</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">in his father's footsteps?</font>

760
01:15:20,415 --> 01:15:23,316  X1:206 X2:513 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">I was gonna say "damned."</font>

761
01:15:23,385 --> 01:15:25,910  X1:244 X2:474 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Of course you were.</font>

762
01:15:25,988 --> 01:15:27,421  X1:254 X2:465 Y1:412 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">But I'm a scientist.</font>

763
01:15:27,489 --> 01:15:31,983  X1:181 X2:537 Y1:348 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">As a scientist,</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">I believe we can figure this out</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">and he can be helped.</font>

764
01:15:32,060 --> 01:15:35,393  X1:072 X2:239 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">I know you do.</font>

765
01:15:35,464 --> 01:15:38,900  X1:073 X2:450 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Look, whether you know or care,</font>

766
01:15:38,967 --> 01:15:42,596  X1:240 X2:479 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">I've got a lot of pride</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">in what you've done.</font>

767
01:15:42,671 --> 01:15:45,663  X1:073 X2:368 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>But this is too big for you.</i></font>

768
01:15:45,741 --> 01:15:49,734  X1:149 X2:569 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Look, I know the government thinks</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">they have a weapon on their hands.</font>

769
01:15:49,811 --> 01:15:52,405  X1:271 X2:647 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Otherwise, he'd be dead by now.</font>

770
01:15:52,481 --> 01:15:54,847  X1:339 X2:633 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>They can probe and prod</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>all they want,</i></font>

771
01:15:54,917 --> 01:15:57,181  X1:205 X2:511 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">and in the meanwhile,</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">just let me try to help him.</font>

772
01:15:57,252 --> 01:16:00,653  X1:072 X2:300 Y1:379 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>Nobody knows him</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>better than I do.</i></font>

773
01:16:03,458 --> 01:16:06,256  X1:070 X2:341 Y1:379 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">What did David Banner</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">do to him?</font>

774
01:16:10,198 --> 01:16:12,098  X1:071 X2:418 Y1:315 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">Cover left!</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">Clear left.</font>

775
01:16:12,167 --> 01:16:14,101  X1:291 X2:427 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Cover right!</font>

776
01:16:14,169 --> 01:16:16,763  X1:464 X2:646 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Siren Wailing]</font>

777
01:16:47,936 --> 01:16:50,598  X1:283 X2:435 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Air Hissing]</font>

778
01:16:55,077 --> 01:16:57,068  X1:304 X2:413 Y1:411 Y2:439
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Inhales]</font>

779
01:17:01,683 --> 01:17:03,674  X1:319 X2:399 Y1:411 Y2:439
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Yells]</font>

780
01:17:26,808 --> 01:17:28,969  X1:072 X2:188 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Panting]</font>

781
01:17:49,931 --> 01:17:51,922  X1:298 X2:420 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Clinking]</font>

782
01:17:54,436 --> 01:17:57,303  X1:294 X2:424 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Creaking]</font>

783
01:18:12,988 --> 01:18:14,979  X1:302 X2:415 Y1:411 Y2:439
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Exhales]</font>

784
01:18:24,800 --> 01:18:27,701  X1:364 X2:648 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">What's happening here?</font>

785
01:18:27,769 --> 01:18:30,260  X1:073 X2:177 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">My hand.</font>

786
01:18:31,707 --> 01:18:35,973  X1:073 X2:322 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>You see, the strength</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>of my son's DNA...</i></font>

787
01:18:36,044 --> 01:18:40,344  X1:213 X2:504 Y1:379 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">combined with nanomed</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">reconstruction...</font>

788
01:18:42,851 --> 01:18:46,844  X1:070 X2:424 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">You see, I can partake</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">with the essences of all things.</font>

789
01:18:48,623 --> 01:18:51,091  X1:339 X2:647 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Gonna have to ask you to...</font>

790
01:18:51,159 --> 01:18:54,185  X1:314 X2:648 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">put your hands up, pal, okay?</font>

791
01:18:54,262 --> 01:18:57,663  X1:072 X2:647 Y1:315 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Nice and easy.</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Creaking]</font>

792
01:18:59,101 --> 01:19:01,035  X1:248 X2:469 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Wheezing Laugh]</font>

793
01:19:02,604 --> 01:19:04,663  X1:073 X2:329 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Do you really believe...</font>

794
01:19:04,740 --> 01:19:09,439  X1:071 X2:404 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">that I am separate from you?</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Laughs]</font>

795
01:19:09,511 --> 01:19:11,809  X1:320 X2:396 Y1:411 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">Whoa!</font>

796
01:19:26,595 --> 01:19:28,586  X1:284 X2:433 Y1:411 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">Where am I?</font>

797
01:19:32,501 --> 01:19:34,435  X1:281 X2:436 Y1:411 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">You're home.</font>

798
01:19:46,782 --> 01:19:49,649  X1:409 X2:647 Y1:379 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">It's hard to believe</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">we used to live here.</font>

799
01:19:52,320 --> 01:19:55,312  X1:071 X2:312 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">I must have seen you</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">or known you.</font>

800
01:19:55,390 --> 01:19:58,223  X1:072 X2:362 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">If only I could remember.</font>

801
01:20:12,507 --> 01:20:15,999  X1:072 X2:303 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Chains Squeaking]</font>

802
01:20:31,960 --> 01:20:34,895  X1:318 X2:648 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">This is my old house, isn't it?</font>

803
01:21:13,468 --> 01:21:15,595  X1:312 X2:407 Y1:412 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Let's go.</font>

804
01:21:17,305 --> 01:21:19,239  X1:073 X2:189 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Please try.</font>

805
01:21:57,045 --> 01:21:59,639  X1:278 X2:439 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Shuddering]</font>

806
01:22:09,124 --> 01:22:11,991  X1:071 X2:365 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>[Shuddering Continues]</i></font>

807
01:22:13,495 --> 01:22:15,554  X1:503 X2:632 Y1:379 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>[Betty]</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>What is it?</i></font>

808
01:22:15,630 --> 01:22:17,564  X1:309 X2:411 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Nothing.</font>

809
01:22:17,632 --> 01:22:19,691  X1:568 X2:648 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Really?</font>

810
01:22:22,070 --> 01:22:24,561  X1:073 X2:171 Y1:412 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>Damn it.</i></font>

811
01:22:29,210 --> 01:22:33,408  X1:310 X2:632 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>Okay, Betty...</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>what do you want to know?</i></font>

812
01:22:36,718 --> 01:22:39,414  X1:070 X2:349 Y1:411 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">What was in that room?</font>

813
01:22:50,265 --> 01:22:53,029  X1:070 X2:444 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">What are you afraid that I'll see?</font>

814
01:22:53,101 --> 01:22:55,035  X1:552 X2:646 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Gasps]</font>

815
01:22:58,273 --> 01:23:02,073  X1:398 X2:647 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">See? There's nothing.</font>

816
01:23:02,143 --> 01:23:05,374  X1:299 X2:419 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Sighs]</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">It's empty.</font>

817
01:23:17,258 --> 01:23:20,022  X1:071 X2:387 Y1:347 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>[Betty]</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>What do you mean,</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>I don't have access to him?</i></font>

818
01:23:20,095 --> 01:23:25,499  X1:071 X2:488 Y1:347 Y2:439
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>[Ross]</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>NSA has decided to turn over study</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>of the, uh...</i> <i>the threat to Atheon.</i></font>

819
01:23:25,567 --> 01:23:28,058  X1:328 X2:647 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">But you're head of the base.</font>

820
01:23:28,136 --> 01:23:30,604  X1:189 X2:529 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">I thought you were in charge.</font>

821
01:23:30,672 --> 01:23:35,302  X1:225 X2:474 Y1:379 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>But I don't set policy,</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>and I still take orders.</i></font>

822
01:23:35,377 --> 01:23:37,607  X1:307 X2:396 Y1:411 Y2:439
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>[Yells]</i></font>

823
01:23:37,679 --> 01:23:41,638  X1:186 X2:530 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">I can't believe Talbot</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">would go around me like this!</font>

824
01:23:43,051 --> 01:23:46,748  X1:154 X2:564 Y1:379 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">Oh, there's a lot of powerful people</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">that want in on this.</font>

825
01:23:46,821 --> 01:23:50,120  X1:335 X2:630 Y1:379 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>And money to be made...</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>lots of it.</i></font>

826
01:23:55,063 --> 01:23:58,328  X1:215 X2:503 Y1:379 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">You know the worst part</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">about all this?</font>

827
01:23:58,400 --> 01:24:01,460  X1:142 X2:559 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>When I had David Banner locked up</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>and sent that kid away,</i></font>

828
01:24:01,536 --> 01:24:05,700  X1:133 X2:585 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">I didn't give that boy a second thought;</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">he was just collateral damage.</font>

829
01:24:05,774 --> 01:24:09,005  X1:190 X2:527 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Well, he isn't anymore, is he?</font>

830
01:24:11,312 --> 01:24:13,246  X1:271 X2:446 Y1:411 Y2:435
<font color="#fdfdfd">What can I do?</font>

831
01:24:13,314 --> 01:24:16,806  X1:226 X2:490 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">[Sighs]</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">You can go home now.</font>

832
01:24:18,753 --> 01:24:21,984  X1:072 X2:474 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>I'd tell you to go and say good-bye,</i></font>
<font color="#fdfdfd"><i>but I've already been informed...</i></font>

833
01:24:22,057 --> 01:24:25,823  X1:179 X2:539 Y1:379 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">that for now all further contact</font>
<font color="#fdfdfd">is out of the question.</font>

834
01:24:27,195 --> 01:24:28,662  X1:326 X2:393 Y1:411 Y2:441
<font color="#fdfdfd">Right.</font>